        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 11 of the SLEEP program. The script targets the sleep identity: not a single bad night but the accumulated belief that poor sleep is simply who you are. A daytime practice for releasing the old story and trying on a quieter one.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
