            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I've called myself a bad sleeper for a long time, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though that label became part of how I see myself, I honour why I held onto it. It helped explain the struggle.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though it feels risky to believe something new, I'm open to releasing this old identity.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
